{"tid":2041380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人去到某一點就想就咁合埋眼乜都唔諗","createTime":"2020-05-29T08:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T10:10:20.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"388af4bd17e17927269891707bd1c130759b030c","tid":2041380,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:03:03.000Z","msg":"家庭<br />\n工作<br />\n前途<br />\n健康<br />\n寵物<br />\n因為無論做咩<br />\n到最後都好似手中沙<br />\n尋晚r頭r出一汁三條白髮<br />\n好似同一條毛囊出<br />\n睇唔清<br />\n有時做人<br />\n連做d令自己輕鬆既野都費事<br />\n因為其實你仲思考緊<br />\n就咁乜都唔諗<br />\n係屋企就訓訓訓<br />\n係出面除左返工就遊巴士河<br />\n以前都會自己有自己世界<br />\n但連依個世界都崩潰<br />\n你一行出街就咩都唔係<br />\n但現實又殘忍<br />\n唯有一片空白<br />\n人地講咩你重覆一次<br />\n人地做咩你照做<br />\n好似影印機咁<br />\n情願咁亦唔想再煩<br />\n因為有主見其實係一件好煩既事黎<br />\n唯一心願<br />\n就係依世人唔好太痛苦"},{"pid":"039cdeb221ee84db880268a4eea96b34471186ed","tid":2041380,"uid":81533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a3d51c6e06e53b4a1cf92a46421818d32b63f4","tid":2041380,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"死?"},{"pid":"c47c78bbd6f342cb2e89c4fe647387eb12679c2e","tid":2041380,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e876230113567f41c9b6ff1d74c087136ee322ea","tid":2041380,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣好鐘意樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5736b26f0921da6742bb4ddf64c3e98939d1874e","tid":2041380,"uid":98678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47c78bbd6f342cb2e89c4fe647387eb12679c2e","tid":2041380,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"773519054fa0d75aff49264aaa8